Quickstrike:




"Ah'm fine," Quickstrike replied to Stingtra. "Jus' need t' lie down." He 
tried to think of what was wrong. He had stepped out of the CR tank a few 
cycles ago, and now he was dizzy and his stomach hurt. He thought. A few 
days ago, his body was put to his limits. Perhaps his systems were telling 
him to slow down. But he didn't like that. Not to mention he had lost a lot 
of weight. He had nearly starved to death a while ago.
